### Key Findings

- **`ai_suggestion` field does not exist** in backend or frontend — suggestion must be sourced from existing `nudges` (filter by `thing_id`) or `proactiveSurfaces` (filter by `thing.id`), both already in the Zustand store
- **Design file trumps issue body**: `code.html` specifies `bg-surface-container-highest/30 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-secondary`, not `bg-surface-container-high rounded-2xl` as the issue text states
- **`openChatWithContext` is ready to use** — already implemented in the store (`store.ts:873`), just needs to be added to `DetailPanel.tsx`'s `useStore` subscription
- **Use `!!aiSuggestion &&` guard** — the `&&` operator is safe for strings but must use boolean cast to avoid accidental rendering of falsy values

### Gaps

- Whether to add `ai_suggestion` to the backend `Thing` model (no such field exists yet), or rely on `nudges`/`proactiveSurfaces` — the issue spec is ambiguous; the nudge/proactive approach requires no backend changes
